com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.wifi

类 WiFiNetworksManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.agilelink.framework.wifi.WiFiNetworksManager

  • public class WiFiNetworksManager
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to add/fetch/update and delete a WiFiNetwork object. For ease of use and quick WiFi setup, AMAP will store SSID and WiFi password once provided using the WiFiNetworksManager addNetwork method. This can be reused if user sets up another device or logs in from another mobile device using the fetchNetworks method.
